com.dhemery.expressions

Interface Named


  • public interface Named
    Factory methods to decorate BooleanSupplier, Predicate, and Function objects to make them self-describing.

                                                     BooleanSupplier supplier)
        Decorates the supplier to describe itself with the given name.
